query:
SELECT 
  CASE 
    WHEN name LIKE '%Vial%' OR name LIKE '%vial%' THEN 'Vials'
    WHEN name LIKE '%Cap%' OR name LIKE '%cap%' THEN 'Caps'
    WHEN name LIKE '%Filter%' OR name LIKE '%filter%' THEN 'Filters'
    WHEN name LIKE '%SPE%' OR name LIKE '%Cartridge%' THEN 'SPE'
    WHEN name LIKE '%GC%' OR name LIKE '%Gas Chromatography%' THEN 'GC'
    WHEN name LIKE '%Guard%' THEN 'Guard'
    WHEN name LIKE '%Column%' OR name LIKE '%column%' THEN 'Columns'
    ELSE 'Other'
  END as product_category,
  COUNT(*) as count
FROM products
GROUP BY product_category
ORDER BY count DESC;
